OL,4,BRoma ban fan for life after racist
OL,5,Babuse of defender Juan Jesus
OL,6, Roma have handed a lifetime ban to a
OL,7, supporter who racially abused Brazilian
OL,8, defender Juan Jesus on social media.
OL,10,FThe Serie A side tweeted an image of
OL,11,Fthe messages - including details of the
OL,12,Faccount - and confirmed they had
OL,13,Freported the incident to the police.
OL,15,FThe public denunciation was met with
OL,16,Fwidespread appreciation on Twitter.
OL,18,FIt comes after anti-discriminatory body
OL,19,FFare said Italian football authorities
OL,20,Fand their disciplinary systems to
OL,21,Fcombat racism were not fit for purpose.
